Call recording uses the operator's conference call function to record calls. If you can't combine calls, please contact the operator to find out if your account supports conference call.
The app only starts recording calls after the beep.
You can try all the available features for free.
Please note that call recording cannot record new calls without a valid subscription, but you can listen to previously recorded calls.
Unlimited access to member subscription
You can subscribe to unlimited access to all functions of call recording.
· subscriptions are charged weekly, monthly, quarterly or annually, depending on the subscription plan selected.
· payment will be deducted from your iTunes account when you confirm your purchase.
· you can turn off automatic renewal 24 hours before the end of the current subscription, otherwise it will be automatically renewed.
· the current subscription will be renewed with a deduction from your account within 24 hours before the end of the subscription, depending on the plan you choose.
The user can manage the subscription and go to the user account to set and turn off the automatic subscription after purchase.
Any unused free subscription time will be void after the user purchases the subscription.
Call recording also provides a lifetime subscription, with unlimited access to call recording.
